OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with patchy cloud and late
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Staying mostly dry with
OL,8,Fclear spells overnight, but an
OL,9,Fisolated light shower possible. Fresh
OL,10,Fnorthwesterly winds becoming westerly.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA largely dry day with sunny
OL,13,Fspells and the odd isolated shower
OL,14,Fpossible. Cloud spreading northwards
OL,15,Finto Orkney in the afternoon. Light
OL,16,Fwesterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
