OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FRemaining unsettled with scattered
OL,7,Fshowers or longer spells of rain at
OL,8,Ftimes spreading eastwards,
OL,9,Finterspersed with drier and brighter
OL,10,Fspells. Often windy.
